<section id="fb1">
	<p align="left"><b>during -> between</b></p>
</section>
<section id="fb2">
	<p align="left"><b>at -> during</b></p>
</section>
<section id="fb3">
	<p align="left"><font color="#000000"><b>in - > from:</b> The period referred to began in 1999 and ended in 2001.</font></p>
</section>
<section id="fb4">
	<p align="left"><font color="#000000"><b>to -> of:</b> The figure fell from 143 million to 138 million. This is a drop of 5 million.</font></p>
</section>
<section id="fb5">
	<p align="left"><b>on -> in</b></p>
</section>
<section id="fb6">
	<p align="left"><font color="#000000"><b>by -> to:</b> This is the level it rose to, not the size of the increase.</font></p>
</section>
<section id="fb7">
	<p align="left"><font color="#000000"><b>before -> by:</b> Note the use of past perfect tense for the main verb, 'had risen' in this sentence.</font></p>
</section>
<section id="fb8">
	<p align="left"><font color="#000000"><b>had been -> were:</b> There is no need for the past perfect tense here.</font></p>
</section>
<section id="fb9">
	<p align="left"><font color="#000000"><b>In -> Between:</b> A period that falls between two dates is referred to here.</font></p>
</section>
<section id="fb10">
	<p align="left"><font color="#000000"><b>to -> by:</b> This is the size of the increase referred to here, not the level the figures reached.</font></p>
</section>
<section id="fb11">
	<p align="left"><font color="#000000"><b>to -> over:</b> 'During this period', in other words.</font></p>
</section>
<section id="fb12">
	<p align="left"><font color="#000000"><b>latter -> former:</b> The former is 'Europe'.</font></p>
</section>
<section id="fb13">
	<p align="left"><font color="#000000"><b>former -> latter:</b> The latter is 'Eurasia'.</font></p>
</section>
<section id="fb14">
	<p align="left"><font color="#000000"><b>to -> by:</b> This is the size of the decrease, not the level the figures fell to.</font></p>
</section>
<section id="fb15">
	<p align="left"><b>had been -> was</b></p>
</section>
<section id="fb16">
	<p align="left"><font face="verdana" size="13" color="#000000">from</font></p>
</section>
<section id="fb17">
	<p align="left"><font face="verdana" size="13" color="#000000">in</font></p>
